{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回\"狮子开头\"，燕十三与慕容秋荻在树林中对峙。慕容秋荻手持枯枝代替剑，想要燕十三拔剑一试。燕十三看穿她的意图——她手中枯枝是死的，没有杀人的渴望，而且她并非谢晓峰本人。燕十三指出慕容秋荻因生育孩子而对谢晓峰既爱又恨，对自己的生命已毫无留恋。燕十三承诺一定找机会杀谢晓峰，并在与慕容秋荻的对峙中领悟出破解三少爷剑法的招式，枯枝一刺便化为粉末。离开树林后，燕十三遇到七岁孩童小讨厌，这孩子精明伶俐，向燕十三索要问话费，燕十三写下五万两欠条。小讨厌告知燕十三的同伴乌鸦去山坡后与曹冰拼命。燕十三赶去发现乌鸦重伤，乌鸦惊叹曹冰使出的一招超越点苍剑法，其变化匪夷所思，连乌鸦这样的高手也无法抵挡。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你为何还不拔剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我的剑已在手，随时都可以拔出来，你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这就是我的剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "这不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "在我手里，这就是杀人的利器。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我知道你能用它杀人，但是它本身却只不过是段枯枝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "只要杀人，枯枝和剑有什么分别？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "它能杀人，可是它并没有杀过人，我的剑却不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "这柄剑跟随我已十九年，死在这柄剑下的，已有六十三个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我知道你杀的人不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "这本来也只不过是柄很平凡的剑，可是现在它已饮过六十三个人的血，六十三个无情的杀手，六十三条厉鬼冤魂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "似乎现在这柄剑本身已有了生命，渴望再能尝到别人的血，渴望别人死在它的剑锋下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "它告诉过你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "它没有，可是我能感觉得到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "感觉到什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "只要它一出鞘，就一定要杀人，有时甚至连我自己都无法控制。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你手里这段枯枝却是死的，绝不会有杀人的渴望，你自己也并不是真的想杀了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "因为你根本也不是谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "现在这片叶子是不是也死了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是它刚刚还在树枝上，还是活的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "人的生命岂非也跟这片叶子一样？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我明白你的意思。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你真的明白？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你为了生育那孩子，一定受了不少苦，所以你对他的爱，绝对比不上你心里的怨恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "所以你对自己的生命已毫无留恋，只要我能破得了这一剑，你就算死在我剑下，也是心甘情愿的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "可是你错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我错了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "因为我就算能破得了你这一剑，也未必能破谢晓峰的剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "因为你用的并不是杀人的剑，你也不是谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "可是我答应你，只要我有机会，我一定杀了他！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你自觉有几成把握？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "本来连一成都没有！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "现在至少已有了四五成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你已想出了破法？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你看着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你去吧。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "快回去吧，你姐姐在等你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "她等我干什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "因为……因为她关心你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "她关心我干什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "难道你认为从来都没有人关心过你？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "从来也没有，连半个人都没有，我是个小讨厌，讨厌我的人倒不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是我一点都不在乎。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "我那朋友呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你哪个朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "乌鸦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "这树林里没有乌鸦，只有麻雀。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "我是说刚才跟我在一起的，那个叫乌鸦的人！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你有没有付我保管费？请我保管他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "既然没有，你凭什么问我！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "因为……因为我想你一定知道他到哪里去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我当然知道，可是我凭什么一定要告诉你？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是我也并不是一定不能告诉你。",
      "tone": "调皮",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "要怎么样你才肯告诉我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你要问我的话，多多少少总得付我一点问话费。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "看你穿得还蛮像样的，难道只不过是个空壳子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "因为从来也没有人要收过我的问话费。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "木头里既然榨不出油来，我也只好认倒楣了，你就写张欠条来吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "欠条？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你要问话，就得付问话费，现在你没钱，以后总会有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "这里又没有纸笔，欠条怎么写？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你的剑削块树皮，再用你的剑把字写在树皮上。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你倒想得真周到。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "写多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "一个字也是写，十个字也是写，既然是欠账，就得多写点。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你就马马虎虎给我写个一万两吧。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我知道你现在心里一定在想，现在我就这么会敲竹帛，长大了怎么得了？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你怎么知道我心里在想什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为这些话已经不知道有多少人问过我了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "现在我就会敲竹帛，长大了当然就是大富翁，这么简单的道理难道你都不懂？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "要一万，给五万，看来你的人虽穷，出手倒不小。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "出手小的人，怎么会穷？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "有理的话，你就应该记在心里，你若不想穷，出手就不能太大方，更不能乱花钱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "有了钱不花干什么？那跟没有钱又有什么分别？",
      "tone": "调皮",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "我现在虽然没钱，可是我随时都会有钱的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我看得出，否则我怎么会收你的欠条。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "你随时看见我，都可以向我收钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "所以你就该把这张字条好好收起来，免得掉了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "掉了就算你走运，我倒楣。那也没什么了不起。",
      "tone": "无所谓",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "就好像你若很快就死了，我也只好自认倒楣一样，像你这种人，本来随时都会死的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "你那个朋友到前面那山坡后去了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "去干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "好像是去拼命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "text": "拼命！去跟谁拼命？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "小讨厌",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "好像是个叫什么冰的小子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "是曹冰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "是不是你故意让他的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我知道你不信，连我自己都不信，我看过那小子出手。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "可是你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我本来有把握可以在三招内让他倒下去的，绝对有把握。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "可是现在倒下去的却是你！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "那只因为我错了！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "哪点错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我看过他出手，他剑法中的变化我也已摸清，点苍派的剑法绝对伤不了我的毫发。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "他用的不是点苍剑法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "绝不是。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "他用的是什么剑法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "连你都看不出？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "那一招的变化，我非但看不出，连想都想不到。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_wu_ya",
      "text": "那一招？他只出手一招，你就伤在他的剑下？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "如果是你，你也一样接不住那一招的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ya",
      "speaker_name": "乌鸦",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "到现在我还想不出有谁能接得住那一招。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    }
